OL,3,CMeat producer launches review after
OL,4,Cpiglet abuse claims
OL,6,FThe UK's biggest pork supplier has
OL,7,Flaunched an independent review into
OL,8,Fclaims of abuse at a Lincolnshire pig
OL,9,Ffarm.
OL,11,FCranswick, based in Hessle in East
OL,12,FYorkshire, suspended its arrangements
OL,13,Fwith Northmoor Farm in response to
OL,14,Fcovert footage appearing to show
OL,15,Fbanned methods being used to slaughter
OL,16,Fanimals.
