OL,3,CMeat producer launches review after
OL,4,Cpiglet abuse claims
OL,6,FThe video, filmed by Animal Justice
OL,7,FProject (AJP), appeared to show
OL,8,Fworkers holding piglets by their hind
OL,9,Flegs and slamming them to the ground,
OL,10,Fin a practice known as "piglet
OL,11,Fthumping".
OL,13,FFollowing the release of the footage,
OL,14,Fretailers including Asda, Morrisons,
OL,15,FSainsbury's and Tesco suspended
OL,16,FNorthmoor Farm as a supplier.
OL,18,FCranswick has already said it will not
OL,19,Fsell on any pigs which were based at
OL,20,Fthe farm.
