OL,3,CMeat producer launches review after
OL,4,Cpiglet abuse claims
OL,6,FChief executive Adam Couch said the
OL,7,Fbusiness is now reviewing its
OL,8,Foperations.
OL,10,F"We take seriously any instance,
OL,11,Fanywhere in our supply chain, where
OL,12,Fbehaviour fails to meet those
OL,13,Fstandards," he said.
OL,15,F"We are therefore instigating a new,
OL,16,Ffully independent, expert veterinarian
OL,17,Freview of all our existing animal
OL,18,Fwelfare policies, together with a
OL,19,Fcomprehensive review of our livestock
OL,20,Foperations across the UK.
