OL,3,CMeat producer launches review after
OL,4,Cpiglet abuse claims
OL,6,F"We will provide a further update on
OL,7,Fthis work in due course."
OL,9,FThe use of blunt force trauma to kill
OL,10,Fpiglets under 10kg was made illegal in
OL,11,F2022 after warnings the method was
OL,12,Funreliable and inhumane.
OL,14,FAbout 6,000 pigs are kept at Northmoor
OL,15,FFarm. Cranswick as a whole slaughters
OL,16,Fmore than 34,000 pigs per week.
