OL,3,CMeat producer launches review after
OL,4,Cpiglet abuse claims
OL,6,FSpeaking last week, AJP founder Claire
OL,7,FPalmer called for "immediate
OL,8,Fenforcement of the ban on blunt force
OL,9,Ftrauma and the prosecution of
OL,10,FCranswick".
OL,12,F"There must be an independent public
OL,13,Finquiry into pig farming practices and
OL,14,Fregulatory failures," she said.
OL,16,FThe review comes as Cranswick revealed
OL,17,Fsales and profits jumped over the past
OL,18,Fyear. Revenues grew by 6.8% to #2.72
OL,19,Fbillion for the year to March,
OL,20,Fcompared with the previous year.
